Former president Jacob Zuma and EFF Leader Julius Malema seem to have put their differences aside. Zuma hosted Malema for tea on Friday. #eNCA Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Former president Jacob Zuma and EFF Leader Julius Malema seem to have put their differences aside. Zuma is hosting Malema for tea on Friday. READ: MKMVA pledges support for Zuma The EFF’s request for tea with Zuma was met with an invitation to Nkandla. Zuma has been under the spotlight for his defiance of a constitutional ruling compelling him to appear before the state capture inquiry.